Comment: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:17.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無法遠離　純白纖細
Comment: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:20.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,危險的愛
Comment: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:25.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,奔跑在滿是慘白
Comment: 0,0:21:25.44,0:21:28.84,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,無限漫長的路上
Comment: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:32.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,為了何人何事
Comment: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:35.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,被追逐著
Comment: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:39.56,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,盡數欲收
Comment: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:44.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目標只有一個
